AutoReq: no

%description
The launcher scripts, native binaries and libraries needed to run the 
Pipeline client programs under Windows XP.  

This RPM should be installed on the same Linux file server as the main 
"pipeline" RPM.  Note that this RPM does not contain the required Java 
classes or data files needed to run the Pipeline client applications.
These resources are accessed over a network share using the path supplied
to the Windows Root Install Directory (--win-root-dir option) to 
plconfig(1) during Pipeline configuration process.

